老闆叫我好好handover d手尾比狗男，但當我諗返3年前佢點對我，我發誓一定唔會比佢有好日子過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係你，黎緊會點做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"這些機會不是屬於我的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打比著我係你就玩撚盡佢，乜都唔hang<br />\n叫親你hang就話唔得閒，last果一兩日就send個表過去叫佢自己跟，個表講到唔清唔楚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都講一半，佢執屎都執撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：公司無限個仆街同事"}]}